Z","msg":"其實係咪用人養啲病毒出黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91eef1c02e926770b82b33b64300f57159accbe6","tid":2171734,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acfc5ad78f5083e1447f765c98ff1765fef1315","tid":2171734,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"拜見習總"},{"pid":"49ac2174f63dd6f16677d5d9b3a2d2ba56c9a947","tid":2171734,"uid":180814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"幾時會爆埋霍亂 痢疾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda828ca6b3865d1683217689cfdfbd942142b97","tid":2171734,"uid":8257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"49ac2174f63dd6f16677d5d9b3a2d2ba56c9a947","tid":2171734,"uid":180814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"幾時會爆埋霍亂 痢疾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:34:44.000Z","msg":"志賀桿菌病（Shigellosis），也稱為桿菌性痢疾（bacillary dysentery）、細菌性痢疾，是一種傳染病，因為攝食了遭志賀氏菌污染的食物或飲水，引發食物中毒。特徵是出血性腹瀉。"},{"pid":"88124e1f61205f163be7162eae0b74383f7332ce","tid":2171734,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb654cac1397abf14b16463dd9e58356a385ba56","tid":2171734,"uid":57205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2018/10/20180510_CH_%E5%8A%9F%E6%88%90%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2018%2F10%2F20180510_CH_%25E5%258A%259F%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25BF%2585%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2588%2591.jpg&h=1152810d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:34:57.000Z","